text.tspan: BICYCLE CRASHES WITH CARS BY CITY
As motorists and bicyclists vie for space on the road, collisions sometimes occur. Here's a breakdown of crashes between cars and bikes as reported
to police in each of the fve cities from 2008 through June 30, 2012.
